Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A product is a product which can be added or modified by administrator or added to shopping cart by shopper or bought by customer. Its information includes:
    • its name
    • the category it belongs to
    • its price
    • An ID generated by system
    • its total quantity
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Derek
